{0 Artifacts}

The artifacts layer renders and exports data produced by the middle-end:

- IR and canonical renderings;
- graph dumps (automata/product/canonical);
- `.kobj` import/export helpers;
- diagnostics and helper outputs.

{1 Scope}

This layer is focused on serialization and presentation of already-computed
semantic data. It does not define proof semantics by itself.

{1 Main areas in the repository}

- `lib/artifacts/ir_render`
  Rendering of canonical IR structures and related views.

- `lib/artifacts/kobj`
  Import/export for Kairos object files (`.kobj`).

- `lib/artifacts/diagnostics`
  Diagnostics materialization helpers.
